OL,3,CLocal elections 2026: The Midlands
OL,4,Cresults
OL,6,FReform UK gained its first council of
OL,7,Fthis year's local elections here in
OL,8,Fthe Midlands, in Newcastle-under-Lyme,
OL,9,Fand in the early hours Redditch went
OL,10,Fto no overall control from Labour,
OL,11,Fwith Reform making large gains.
OL,13,FOvernight, in Dudley, the party won a
OL,14,Ftotal of 22 seats, making gains from
OL,15,Fthe Conservatives, Labour, the Liberal
OL,16,FDemocrats and the Black Country Party
OL,17,F- as well as holding on to their own
OL,18,Fseats.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
