CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1778270754
OL,3,CLocal elections 2026: The Midlands
OL,4,Cresults
OL,6,FThe Conservatives were only able to
OL,7,Fhold onto two of their seats out of
OL,8,Fthe 25 being contested, with Labour
OL,9,Fholding on to one - the rest went to
OL,10,FReform UK.
OL,12,FFor other councils which have already
OL,13,Fdeclared in the Midlands, many have no
OL,14,Foverall control, as a result of Reform
OL,15,FUK making gains.
OL,17,FAnalysis from ITV Central's political
OL,18,Freporter Lewis Warner
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
